div.p:
650. With results all 95 districts announced, following is parties
                                standing in order gains, losses, total: UNP 23, 12, 54; Freedom Party 6, 6, 9; LSSP 1, 6, 9;
                                Front 0, 2, 4; Tamil Cong 0, 1, 4;
                                Federalist 1, 1, 2; Moors 2, 0, 2; Labor 1, 1, 1; Peoples Republican
                                0, 1, 1; Independents including speaker 5, 2, 9. Of 7 former Indian
                                    Cong seats, UNP won 6, Labor 1.
